{"agent_id":"79Ig","agent_seq":86,"timestamp":"2026-07-22T17:04:29.967845Z","event":{"type":"CommentAdded","issue_uuid":"9242e6c2-32a3-45f1-8478-d1fec3a8ce8b","comment_uuid":"f017d4ab-9920-4f68-9c38-f2d5cd16672a","author":"79Ig","content":"CI green on feature/76-marking (run 29940603896): Lint, Test ubuntu/macos/windows, cargo-audit, self-validate all pass. Marking discipline COMPLETE for the output forms that exist (TTY + JSON): partition renderer + Finding.quoted machinery (113ffe5), E0050 schema-violation marking via kind-reconstruction (6f6c3d7), DSL interpolation marking (feaa753). Both adopter-content sites carry document content out-of-line; verified by driving the CLI (invalid enum -> = found: block; unexpected key -> = unexpected: at the key's line). Ready for --no-ff merge. REMAINING (separate issue): compact-verify rendering of quoted regions = #44, which needs the deferred per-finding size-limit number (SO decision) + line-boundary truncation/elision. Also surfaced #77 (verify ignores config.yaml file_globs -> self-validation walks non-corpus dirs).","created_at":"2026-07-22T17:04:29.952183Z","kind":"result","signed_by":"SHA256:u0VtJEsnHrvNPG5QQKKfDO+Rro/KT/xZqEvahzZTqEA","signature":"U1NIU0lHAAAAAQAAADMAAAALc3NoLWVkMjU1MTkAAAAgOk7MLoVvSEPAWM9VkHKFnHq8O1iEkPSfqY7zLc4I28oAAAARY3Jvc3NsaW5rLWNvbW1lbnQAAAAAAAAABnNoYTUxMgAAAFMAAAALc3NoLWVkMjU1MTkAAABA+fHIxd3JjQ5kTe1JYofDGK1JvPGSJiX14pKh1tGIRscyLLqF2IReEA4PxLFoeVD95ZK66dyH4XmDeztRFC9qBw=="},"signed_by":"SHA256:u0VtJEsnHrvNPG5QQKKfDO+Rro/KT/xZqEvahzZTqEA","signature":"U1NIU0lHAAAAAQAAADMAAAALc3NoLWVkMjU1MTkAAAAgOk7MLoVvSEPAWM9VkHKFnHq8O1iEkPSfqY7zLc4I28oAAAAPY3Jvc3NsaW5rLWV2ZW50AAAAAAAAAAZzaGE1MTIAAABTAAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAQJaIjytB0ePgrohp1FC2a3pskZ0DBRgYK6VFewotzOEICDkVTibvl4WaBYQHyG2Qq5guWfVBkxLiV+pjtHRu4w8="}
